# Module: `packages/excalidraw`

- Public API surface is `index.tsx` — do not expose internals
- Component props must be documented with JSDoc
- Do not import from `excalidraw-app/` — dependency only flows downward

## How to verify

- `grep -r "from.*excalidraw-app" packages/excalidraw/` — should return nothing
- Check `index.tsx` exports — only intentionally public symbols should be listed
- `yarn build:packages` — type errors surface missing JSDoc or broken exports
